'''克劳奇山站'''（{{lang-en|Crouch Hill railway station}}）是[[伦敦地上铁|伦敦地上铁]][[福音橡至柏京綫|福音橡至柏京綫]]的一座车站，位于[[伦敦|伦敦]]的[[伊斯靈頓區|伊斯靈頓區]]，属于第3收费区。

==概况==
本站拥有2个站台，1站台去往[[福音橡站|福音橡站]]方向，2站台去往[[巴金站|巴金站]]方向。车站不设售票处，但设有2台自动售票机和2个[[蠔卡|蠔卡]]充值机，每个站台各有1台。每个站台各设有一个避难所，可以通过楼梯到达站台层<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nationalrail.co.uk/stations/CRH/details.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-01-02 |archive-date=2017-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102172600/http://www.nationalrail.co.uk/stations/CRH/details.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但车站目前没有安装电梯的计划。

==列車服務==
*西行列車至[[福音橡站|福音橡站]]，每小時4班<ref name=GOBLtimetable>{{Cite web |url=https://www.tfl.gov.uk/cdn/static/cms/documents/gospel-oak-to-barking-timetable-december-2014.pdf |title= Gospel Oak to Barking timetable |accessdate=2017-01-02 |archive-date=2015-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213065258/http://www.tfl.gov.uk/cdn/static/cms/documents/gospel-oak-to-barking-timetable-december-2014.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*東行列車至[[巴金站|巴金站]]，每小時4班<ref name=GOBLtimetable />

==其他==
隨著途徑本站的列車數量增加，而2節編組的[[內燃動車組|內燃動車組]]已經不能滿足日益增長的客流需求<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.camdennewjournal.com/news/2010/mar/%E2%80%98overcrowded%E2%80%99-trains-danger-gospel-oak-barking-line |title=‘Overcrowded’ trains danger on Gospel Oak to Barking line |accessdate=2017-01-02 |archive-date=2015-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150210182543/http://www.camdennewjournal.com/news/2010/mar/%E2%80%98overcrowded%E2%80%99-trains-danger-gospel-oak-barking-line |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本站在2016年6月開始進行電氣化工程，預計2017年12月結束<ref>[https://www.networkrail.co.uk/news/2016/feb/vital-work-paves-way-GOBE/ "Vital work paves the way for electrification of the Gospel Oak to Barking line"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.networkrail.co.uk/news/2016/feb/vital-work-paves-way-GOBE/ |date=20160630154839 }}''Network Rail'' press release 1 February 2106; Retrieved 23 May 2016</ref>。

